パッケージorg.apache.hadoop.record.compiler.generatedの説明

(DEPRECATED) This package contains code generated by JavaCC from the Hadoop record syntax file rcc.jj. For details about the record file syntax please @see org.apache.hadoop.record.

DEPRECATED: Replaced by Avro.
